## Documentation SSOT Rules

- **DO NOT CREATE**: `PLAN.md`, `TODO.md`, `PHASES.md`, `DONE.md`
- **Task tracking**: `.c4/tasks.db` via `c4_add_todo` (NOT TodoWrite)

